room_title: Escape room "The Search for the Jade Skull" by Cloak and Dagger Escape Rooms in Princeton
room_description: The Jade Skull was a source of unimaginable power during the reign of the Aztecs. The holder of the skull never lost in battle! The skull was thought to be lost forever, however, is now known to be hidden in an Aztec tomb. You and your team must venture deep into the tomb to find the skull before the bad guys get their hands on it!
